Dear {2},

Thanks for registering in Pay[in] system. For security reasons, we need to validate this email is yours. For this reason, we have sent this mail with this link where you have to click:

https://control.pay-in.es/Account/ConfirmEmail

If you want to confirm your registration pasting the user Id and the code in the corresponding boxes:


User Id : {0}


Code : {1}


If you have received this email by mistake or you have not registered in Pay[in] system, ignore and delete this mail from your inbox.

Thank you very much!

Thank you very much!
